  "decision_conditions": [
    "REASON: The proposed roof extension would be harmful to the appearance of the property and particularly the terrace in which it is situated and would fail to respect the principles laid out in section 2.4.2 of the statutory Urban Design Guide (2006) by disrupting the unaltered roofline of the subject section of the terrace, to the detriment of the appearance of the surrounding conservation area.  The proposal would conflict with policies D1 (Overall Design), D4 (Designing in Context), D11 (Alterations and Extensions), D22 (New Development) and D25 (Roof Extensions) of the Islington Unitary Development Plan (2002)."
